{"about_the_game":"<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The operation of this game is very unique. It is recommended to watch the How-to- play video at the top of the page before trying it.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a minesweeper game from a third-person perspective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Marking all mines is the task of each level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/01-minesweeper.gif?t=1736992525\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Minefields may be covered by obstacles and can be cleared by blasting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/02-bomb.gif?t=1736992525\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the levels, you will encounter guards who prevent your action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You have a wealth of skills to fight them,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hand-to-hand combat is your basic skill.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/03-kick.gif?t=1736992525\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lightning is a great way to hit a single target at medium to long range.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/04-Lightning.gif?t=1736992525\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Blastwaves can be used against multiple targets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/06-Blastwave.gif?t=1736992525\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sniper aiming is sometimes necessary.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/05-sniper.gif?t=1736992525\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Yes, you can even fly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are many more skills that you are welcome to experience for yourself once you enter the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a game that pays homage to Minesweeper, Bomberman, Tetris, and believe that you deserve it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/\u6d77\u9614\u5929\u7a7a.gif?t=1736992525\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736992525","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/page.bg.jpg?t=1736992525","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/48da02b766b2b6212a40b2d28f7a75df6bdc25ed/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736992525","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/48da02b766b2b6212a40b2d28f7a75df6bdc25ed/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736992525","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3214770,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The operation of this game is very unique. It is recommended to watch the How-to- play video at the top of the page before trying it.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a minesweeper game from a third-person perspective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Marking all mines is the task of each level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/01-minesweeper.gif?t=1736992525\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Minefields may be covered by obstacles and can be cleared by blasting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/02-bomb.gif?t=1736992525\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the levels, you will encounter guards who prevent your action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You have a wealth of skills to fight them,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hand-to-hand combat is your basic skill.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/03-kick.gif?t=1736992525\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lightning is a great way to hit a single target at medium to long range.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/04-Lightning.gif?t=1736992525\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Blastwaves can be used against multiple targets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/06-Blastwave.gif?t=1736992525\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sniper aiming is sometimes necessary.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/05-sniper.gif?t=1736992525\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Yes, you can even fly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are many more skills that you are welcome to experience for yourself once you enter the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a game that pays homage to Minesweeper, Bomberman, Tetris, and believe that you deserve it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/extras/\u6d77\u9614\u5929\u7a7a.gif?t=1736992525\" /></p>","developers":["SHEN YI"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198820/